[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;64r\u001b8\u001bM\u001b[1;67r\u001b[2;1H"]
[0.000, "o", "; we recommend these changes in PHP's behavior.\r"]
[0.030, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;64r\u001b8"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001bM\u001b[1;67r\u001b[2;1H"]
[0.000, "o", "; Please see the actual settings later in the document for more details as to why\r"]
[0.029, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001bM\u001b[1;67r\u001b[2;1H"]
[0.001, "o", "; or development versions of the INIs with respect to PHP's default behavior.\r"]
[0.029, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;64r\u001b8"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001bM\u001b[1;67r\u001b[2;1H"]
[0.000, "o", "; The following are all the settings which are different in either the production\r"]
