[0.001, "o", "\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H|\u001b[64;33HHowever, this may cause high memory usage, especially if you run\r"]
[0.029, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8\u001b[65d"]
[0.001, "o", "\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H|\u001b[64;33Ha lot of SQL queries ... disable this to avoid that problem.\r"]
[0.042, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8\u001b[65d"]
[0.000, "o", "\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H|\b"]
[0.026, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8\u001b[65d"]
[0.001, "o", "\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H| The $active_group variable lets you choose which connection group to\r"]
[0.029, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8\u001b[65d"]
[0.000, "o", "\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H| make active.  By default there is only one group (the 'default' group).\r"]
[0.030, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8\u001b[65d"]
